headline: New Eagle™ Introduces CODESYS® Support on Production ECUs, Expanding Software Flexibility for Off-Highway and Industrial Markets
summary: New Eagle™, a leader in embedded control systems for intelligent vehicles and machines, today announced software support for CODESYS® across its rugged electronic control units (ECUs), beginning with the John Deere M-series Controllers. The release marks a strategic expansion of New Eagle's embedded ecosystem, bringing greater programming flexibility to OEMs and developers in off-highway, utility, and industrial vehicle markets.

headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks with Impressive Fundamentals and 1 to Keep Off Your Radar
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.
